cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of machine learning for semantic segmentation of CT scans, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also evaluates the usability of an interactive annotation tool, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of machine learning for medical imaging is also a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper mentions the use of suggestions provided by the GUI, which suggests the use of machine learning algorithms for user modeling (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the agreement between readers in classifying healthy and affected lung parenchyma, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
